Dear All,

The biggest sporting event of the year is ready to kick off on the 26th of
September.

Sportsfest, IIT Madras' annual inter-collegiate invitational tournament
sees the institute teams gearing up to face the best Chennai has to offer,
as a prelude to Inter IIT. Football, Hockey, Volleyball, Table Tennis,
Badminton, Basketball and Tennis will find the best of the best giving it
their all to take home the trophy. Be there to support your institute
players, at the respective play fields/courts and show them that they're
not alone.

Best regards,
*Sethu Madhavan A*
